OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FManchester City sealed a domestic
OL,7,Fdouble after Khadija Shaw and Alex
OL,8,FGreenwood inspired the Women's Super
OL,9,FLeague champions to a 4-0 victory over
OL,10,FBrighton in their Wembley FA Cup final.
OL,12,FJamaica striker Shaw, the WSL's Golden
OL,13,FBoot winner for three straight
OL,14,Fseasons, nodded home Greenwood's cross
OL,15,Fin the 38th minute ` her first goal
OL,16,Fsince announcing a four-year contract
OL,17,Fextension on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
