PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FCaptain Greenwood made it two from a
OL,7,Fstoppage-time free-kick to double
OL,8,Ftheir lead before the break, despite a
OL,9,Fvery promising opening half from first-
OL,10,Ftime FA Cup finalists Brighton, in
OL,11,Fsearch of a maiden major trophy.
OL,13,FAoba Fujino added a third in the 66th
OL,14,Fminute, and second-half substitute
OL,15,FVivianne Miedema marked her return to
OL,16,FAndree Jeglertz's line-up for the
OL,17,Ffirst time since March with their
OL,18,Ffourth to put their 400th competitive
OL,19,Fmatch as a professional side to bed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
