OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FThree-time FA Cup champions City were
OL,7,Fappearing in their fifth final, and
OL,8,Ftheir first since losing to Chelsea in
OL,9,Fextra time four years ago.
OL,11,FGoalkeeper Khiara Keating, called up
OL,12,Fto Sarina Wiegman's England squad on
OL,13,FWednesday, was unavailable after
OL,14,Fsustaining an injury in training
OL,15,Fearlier in the week, so it was Ayaka
OL,16,FYamashita between the posts for City.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FBrighton showed intent from the start,
OL,7,Fand City nearly got themselves into
OL,8,Ftrouble when Jade Rose left the ball
OL,9,Ffor her keeper, oblivious to the
OL,10,Fthreat of the lurking Madison Haley,
OL,11,Fwho then collided with Yamashita.
OL,13,FYamashita stayed down and the ball
OL,14,Fcame out to Marisa Olislagers, who
OL,15,Ffired at the open goal but was denied
OL,16,Fan opener by Greenwood's clearance off
OL,17,Fthe line.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FBrighton keeper Chiamaka Nnadozie was
OL,7,Fcalled into action with a smart save,
OL,8,Fbut the Seagulls dominated the
OL,9,Ffollowing 10 minutes, though they were
OL,10,Ftoo tentative and could not make their
OL,11,Fchances count.
OL,13,FCity came to life after the half hour,
OL,14,Ftesting Nnadozie before Shaw broke the
OL,15,Fdeadlock with five minutes remaining
OL,16,Fin the first half, instigated by
OL,17,FGreenwood's lovely looped delivery and
OL,18,Fbeating the rising keeper to plant
OL,19,Fhome a header.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FGreenwood then took matters into her
OL,7,Fown hands, curling a free-kick into
OL,8,Fthe bottom-right corner in the sixth
OL,9,Fminute of stoppage time at the end of
OL,10,Fthe first half.City were three goals
OL,11,Fto the good in the 66th minute.
OL,13,FA well-worked move saw Shaw cut the
OL,14,Fball back to Miedema, who laid it off
OL,15,Ffor the Japan international to curl
OL,16,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
