PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780333563
OL,3,CManchester City seal domestic double
OL,4,Cwith FA Cup victory
OL,6,FMiedema, out since late March for
OL,7,Fpersonal reasons, and whose mother is
OL,8,Fbattling cancer, nodded home City's
OL,9,Ffourth with three minutes remaining in
OL,10,Fnormal time to wrap up the win.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
